# ============================================================
# Environment variables — copy this file to `.env` and fill in
# the values you need. `.env` is gitignored; only this template
# is tracked.
#
# Astro inlines `PUBLIC_*` values into the static client bundle
# at build time, so do not put secrets behind that prefix.
# ============================================================

# Formspree endpoint for the contact form (RF-11). When unset,
# the form gracefully falls back to a `mailto:` action and submits
# open the user's email client instead. Configure it in production
# via the Vercel project's "Environment variables" panel.
#
# Get yours at https://formspree.io/forms after creating a form.
PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=
